{"tid":247674,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人答我 點解一定要領養？","createTime":"2017-05-18T03:55:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T22:43:01.000Z","uid":115621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7844939f28dcad99aa1ab8a343c82bcb436caca9","tid":247674,"uid":115621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eafcb87c139abd3af8406d367400809aa30bf7a","tid":247674,"uid":37110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:02:18.000Z","msg":"以購買代替領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc9acb8f900d330515a48b18743f8ad5156c76e","tid":247674,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T07:22:16.000Z","msg":"無話一定既...<br />\n<br />\npet shop成日都有病狗病貓賣..<br />\n<br />\n你鍾意咪買囉.."},{"pid":"e4e280b5b8cda1ae59fb2209314e5287b78f01de","tid":247674,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無話一定既...<br />\n<br />\npet shop成日都有病狗病貓賣..<br />\n<br />\n你鍾意咪買囉..</blockquote><br />\n如果肯比錢<br />\n唔使買呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大把人買，個個都買病貓病狗？<br />\n<br />\n領養返黎有情緒病貓狗<br />\n你即係返多份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9681c642128df53eab66dd118ed44f9fa26d28b6","tid":247674,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:38:44.000Z","msg":"可能我有啲過份<br />\n如果我要領養<br />\n一定要領養一隻俾前主人虐待過既<br />\n因為啲貓太高竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望前主人打到隻貓聽聽話話<br />\n然後俾貓異工發現<br />\n我再領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf29596d3200157b2ed6b668286c2ba06006bff","tid":247674,"uid":8458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:41:01.000Z","msg":"唔一定要領養，如果係一定既就無人買貓狗"},{"pid":"85100527f286c94ac312b2512c0f2eada50e3c19","tid":247674,"uid":109302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T17:53:47.000Z","msg":"無話一定嘅，如果你中意名種嘅咪去買囉，<br />\n因為放得出㴝比人領養通常都唔會有名種，就算有嘅大多數都已經年老/有病 (以我嘅觀察啦)<br />\n無病又後生嘅名種啲義工點會放出㴝比人領養呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一早內部認購曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都打算領養<br />\n不過我因為撚開港短(姐係普通唐貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n所以我自己都想領養番隻唐貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我真係覺得無論領養同買都無咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係每個人嘅選擇姐<br />\n成日見到啲人互相批鬥真係覺得好無語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6519742153339ffcdd366521e8163801622e9014","tid":247674,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T14:14:21.000Z","msg":"需求問題多人買自然會生產更多近親或病貓"},{"pid":"c1294dc71f8822572ef3e5fe3514dc83d363eb1d","tid":247674,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:34:13.000Z","msg":"我條條魚都真金白銀買返黎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9703ed38075d6f567c58b89381981d25340a1c","tid":247674,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T19:07:33.000Z","msg":"因為領養先有機會俾班貓義工篩走堆想養貓既窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c672ae0b094ff49a37e3e038facaa602078689ed","tid":247674,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T22:43:01.000Z","msg":"肯比心機少少實會搵到正常寵物店<br />\n妖魔化哂所有買賣寵物根本就on9"}]}